<title>定义矩阵设置别名/条码</title>
</head>
<body id="maintab-body">
将针对选中的规格m和颜色n进行m x n个条码生成。如果删除已存在的规格或颜色，相应的条码也将都尝试被删除。
如果条码已经被使用，删除动作将失败。
<div id="tabs">
<ul>
<li><a href="#tab0" title="tab0"><span>选择颜色</span></a></li>
<li><a href="#tab1" title="tab1"><span>选择规格</span></a></li>
</ul>
<div id="tab0"><!-- start size tab -->
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" width="400" height="316" align="center">
<tr>
	<td width="173"  height="117">
		所有颜色<br>
		<SELECT id="all_colors" class="selectbox" MULTIPLE size="25" ondblclick="mx.addColor()"></SELECT>
	</td>
	<td width="25" valign="top"><div class="mv">
		<input type="button" value=">" onclick="mx.addColor()"/> <p>
		<input type="button" value="<" onclick="mx.removeColors()"/> <p>
	</td>
	<td width="173"  height="117">
		当前选中颜色<br>
		<SELECT id="sel_colors" class="selectbox" MULTIPLE size="25" ondblclick="mx.removeColors()"></SELECT>
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td width="173"  align="left">
		<div id="lc">
			<input type="button" name="listcolors" value="列出所有颜色" onclick="mx.listColors()">
		</div>
	</td>
	<td>&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="173">
		<FIELDSET><LEGEND>手工新增颜色</LEGEND>
  		输入: <input type="text" name="inscolor" id="inscolor" size="12" value="" onkeypress="mx.checkColor(event)"><br>
  		信息: <span id="colormsg"></span>
		</FIELDSET>
	</td>
</tr>

</table>	
</div><!-- end size tab -->
<div id="tab1"><!-- start color tab -->
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" width="400" height="316" align="center">
<tr>
	<td width="173"  height="117">
		所有规格<br>
		<SELECT id="all_specs" class="selectbox" MULTIPLE size="25" ondblclick="mx.addSpec()"></SELECT>
	</td>
	<td width="25" valign="top"><div class="mv">
		<input type="button" value=">" onclick="mx.addSpec()"/> <p>
		<input type="button" value="<" onclick="mx.removeSpecs()"/> <p>
	</td>
	<td width="173"  height="117">
		当前选中规格<br>
		<SELECT id="sel_specs" class="selectbox" MULTIPLE size="25" ondblclick="mx.removeSpecs()"></SELECT>
	</td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td width="173"  align="left">
		<div id="ls">
			<input type="button" name="listspecs" value="列出所有规格" onclick="mx.listSpecs()">
		</div>
	</td>
	<td>&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="173">
		<FIELDSET><LEGEND>手工新增规格</LEGEND>
  		输入: <input type="text" name="insspec" id="insspec" size="12" value="" onkeypress="mx.checkSpec(event)"><br>
  		信息: <span id="specmsg"></span>
		</FIELDSET>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div><!-- end color tab -->

</div>
<script>
jQuery('#tabs ul').tabs();
</script>
<div id="btns">
	<input type="button" name="save" value="生成条码" onclick="mx.save()">
	<input type="button" name="cancel" value="取消" onclick="mx.cancel()">
</div>
